{"hd2031514gc120g4e30g9923gd32fdf15fe3b": ["Arka, wait! You can't just shoot her - ", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "0dd4a5a6-11b7-fd1b-54bb-84838fa499d4"], "h7a4f403bge2b0g4377ga040gba05eaab7b99": ["Why not? That's what her kind did to Kanon.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "ee757910-d18a-8020-be51-3183d060ab1a"], "h60e35257gf467g4be1g9321gedc21c8854df": ["Ya ain't gonna shoot me. Yer hands are shakin'. ", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "18b47eeb-97ed-a69a-92a6-b8645dca8ec4"], "hd6b44c96g9e32g4680gb7d0g70def87a8d9e": ["Ya ain't gonna shoot me. Yer hands are shakin'. ", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "7542e40a-a5d4-5558-3a8b-d217eb290f04"], "h40dd2995gef94g4930ga897g87fdb74c3c69": ["Put it down. She can't fight back. ", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "92c7a5c2-9e44-a743-45e1-95ac1bd4fbc3"], "h3431d08agf639g4e45g866agdf9add6d685d": ["That's the point. Get out of the way.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "a5178892-b333-eb2d-576b-c1acde8110ac"], "hc6ac0ad8gaa52g41e5g810fgaf6fed9724c9": ["She didn't kill your brother, Arka. You're better than this. ", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "655ce4bc-e82d-f781-33d2-dfe97974d91b"], "hec1c20bbg81dcg4e50gae89g924be026b209": ["Shoot before you lose your nerve, tiefling. If you ever had it to begin with. ", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "4c2aefd3-ad7e-9226-fcad-1345202fd50b"], "h92f3a09egc9fcg439cg8e8fgfa7d06effccf": ["Shut up. Those words could be your last.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "7dbcc490-7994-3736-a9fb-8cef8542e181"], "ha83b24d9g46f1g4f2dg9bc3ga443d479e66e": ["I'm not afraid. Chosen by the Absolute, I am. I'm <i>blessed</i>. ", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "ab1fe499-079c-cf2d-69fb-0a7f8d6dd1b6"], "h35c03eacgb8efg48acgb1eeg51aa7c52145e": ["Oh, I'll bless you all right. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "d62aab60-30d8-25d6-091e-f59e26bdb095"], "h4f489725g87eeg4cbeg9050geb80efa59c62": ["<i>Move in front of the tiefling's crossbow.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "9ad348a6-5fab-13e4-cb9f-cc0354849b71"], "h7f8b9412gafd5g4419gb41bgad07f5090d06": ["<i>Watch what happens.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "5251f917-62ea-6f8e-fc1b-3553585e1b77"], "hdf040eb0gcaf0g4ffeg8a39gba4e16860888": ["<i>Step between the crossbow and the goblin.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "dcbd7c63-66e1-f250-576e-d07fe5641a55"], "h80482d48g2276g4a38g945cg25bddb7dec5e": ["Looks like the Absolute sent me a protector. Ya gonna kill 'er too?", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "401848a4-bc9d-f63b-8d3c-096031ead157"], "h8e46e8b3g177eg4119g951cgb0a5d95c4b8e": ["Looks like the Absolute sent me a protector. Ya gonna kill 'im too?", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "401848a4-bc9d-f63b-8d3c-096031ead157"], "hd12ca1b6g1979g425dg94e0gb50778550d82": ["You! Move!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "24fa4618-b72c-4af9-7e14-0129de2ad3f9"], "h0f2a2c71gdfc8g475dgaa7bg7c7490eb6420": ["What would Kanon think of you now?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "39228dbd-21d3-d907-8b27-846ee1b51b0d"], "hd995e279g003eg43ffga7c2g9f379d4da692": ["Don't you <i>dare</i>!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "3ccada4f-23da-df4f-88cd-19eb66f349c1"], "h5e2a3de2g7150g4d5eg9b3egdcbd235cd740": ["Damn you. Damn it!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "a5133aa7-45ac-7549-4602-7281acef94f1"], "hdaec3a35gab2dg42c2gbfe8g0da4d30db498": ["Why do you care if a goblin lives or dies?", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "17f87ef5-1247-06c6-05c2-730f8b227605"], "hbe2989a1g8456g4310gaaf8gb2da5ae131b8": ["Because she's not a practice target. She's a person.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "6ec22459-605a-2027-7975-ecd8fa2d89ed"], "h3d44ed2egb6abg4f2dgb050g4a2daa647b2f": ["<i>Tsk. </i>Your soft heart will be the death of us.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "fa335242-fda1-eee8-b2ff-b60441d57294"], "h169321ecg9615g4d05gbbd0g7e766e481589": ["Can't say I understand that. Not sure I want to. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "42eeb1bf-569f-332c-7867-07dc9f5368db"], "h436ca21fg3f75g4dbbgbe44gb2b904acd15e": ["It's all right, Arka. Let's go. ", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "341bdf35-7e56-0dbf-9414-f7aa84f7f372"], "h85ff58c5g4b67g4850g9309g1f17ca4acb22": ["She's all yours. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "eb7e2bd0-510d-905d-aa9a-3665f2eb1a79"], "h87cdea89g6e6fg4fe0gb8f7g2e6ee2ea2552": ["If she dies, she'll take everything she knows to the grave.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "b93f39d1-a5c0-7411-c385-25d44e6bdead"], "h225fd333g606ag48dagbf46g0e0abab3cacc": ["If you believe anything the beast tells you, you're an idiot.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "0f638744-79bb-d502-dc2e-9c35691b5abc"], "hc01a17c7gb172g4f41ga1edg7f23999cdb56": ["A goblin <i>prisoner</i>. Her life isn't yours to take.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "827e9252-7808-13b6-9067-ffc7fb379ae1"], "h677e7c45geadag4df7g9fd5g3c0ea841a90a": ["Not sure I get that. The bars don't make her special. But, fine, whatever.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "b34b7792-f1f6-1f75-530b-daad33cf2537"], "h70baa763g8488g40f3g8147g9bb25fe3e36d": ["Because vengeance eats people alive. You'll grant the goblins two victories this day.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "510ce4b9-b615-c21d-d3f9-a3e236c29afd"], "hc6108cf7g6c69g4b34g9d6agc3e30f57196b": ["You'd better be right. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "6eb752ee-1d1e-0261-da31-ab7a2dd9896d"], "h222667abg6193g4219gba65gcbf8ce362709": ["My reasons are my own.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "5b2c8d7e-43f4-2422-3360-948aee0497f1"], "hfa1752d0gb65fg496fg8291g252abbd499ef": ["Gods, you're exhausting. Fine, then. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "e97a0211-c156-d25d-0a3c-69d2231a962c"], "hedc7a726g5bc3g4fc6gb57eg14ba1ff49d4d": ["No, shoot me. Should be easy, right?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "850ce384-de3e-bf62-3a07-099c242c7197"], "h2af4a695g2929g454egad55g8758164d39ce": ["What in every Hell is wrong with you?", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "68782ddd-0823-41a5-e733-2de3d4644a95"], "h7a876cd3g08b8g416fg8a1ag01e4b2d017e4": ["You fought for us, so I'll give you one last chance. <i>Move.</i>", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "6b800384-2a53-f9de-9530-ca301c038812"], "h13b08157gafedg434dg810fg6536c6640438": ["Lower the crossbow, or I'll deliver you right to your brother.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "ae45f397-8c15-f82e-ec40-0a8a6d53ce26"], "h55816fefg1043g40a2gbd30g35f314e45112": ["You want to die for this stupid goblin? Fine.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "ffd4dc30-1f28-1017-ea4a-d8e439cdb15c"], "he0d683d7gb7a6g4190g9aafgd3fa4bfd5d5d": ["This won't avenge Kanon. It won't change anything.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "d1c2fd85-06dd-45ec-4778-3639312d593c"], "he426681dg0c09g448egad8dg6b2146a8db23": ["You're right. I wish you weren't, I really do. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "29fa1474-e1f7-05af-4df5-a7bab3288757"], "ha87085ccg6dc9g4908g99d6g6a9561dec4b5": ["Who cares?", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "023382e4-d948-55e4-d517-02e83228ebf4"], "h7d3c8f7dg5eb0g463eg85bbg896623dba266": ["Killing this goblin won't help you. Let the gods provide comfort.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "9ad04814-b6f8-19bf-158d-47e6d0d6f0c0"], "h13a87232g79f2g4b7bga60fg939169f6aad9": ["Comfort? Is that what you think I'm after? ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "4f432963-5a17-da5d-8f34-c8a2a7ce70d8"], "h1a06d83cgdb4dg4b7bga5ebgee2a2369b501": ["Never mind. Don't answer that. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "333a7152-18eb-1b85-9d2a-e7956602fd6f"], "h6fe3442ag160eg48f3gb9cag5c6fd8385bd1": ["I'm not looking for miracles. Just blood.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "8a529c63-0b17-4e3a-f980-14e63f26e3b4"], "h6856e245gf127g4402gb477g96e5d6965558": ["<i>Read the tiefling's thoughts.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "2ad81493-a8ef-8ea4-b354-54889e5133a8"], "hbb78ad8ag1906g4b0ega364gb4b5d2ca2949": ["<i>Kanon would hate me for this. But he's not here. They took him from me.</i>", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "cd88b344-30ca-a3f2-e13f-21f9e9996ab4"], "h63c28484g597dg429egac17g4b5970f97618": ["Ugh... stop it! Get out of my head!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "1783e106-e19d-20c7-235c-e90f36037cea"], "hf25aa7c4g83ecg47c6g911fg5aa20ab59753": ["<i>Step out of the way.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "a8835d64-57ba-80c9-63cd-91ebc49f858c"], "h2916af87g17a8g4f15gaf83g1d3b62436bda": ["Smart choice. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "7e1aa07b-6f64-2266-7dd8-b01803b538c1"], "hf51ca831gbf5cg4657g8696geb1c48693088": ["Here it comes, you little beast. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "051fceb8-b9c1-4b0a-1bed-f82d0d74f565"], "h1d6ff44cg3da4g46a7g847cg33ab2097e631": ["<i>Do nothing.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "a54f3b3d-054e-6acd-b44a-0d1c44fe3d83"], "hc5c0e8c5gdae0g406dg971cg4364d6e059e9": ["Doesn't even matter if ya kill me. I'm chosen by the Absolute, I am. I'm <i>blessed</i>. ", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "074f200b-e5a6-d2b0-8b91-3e759bc892ff"], "hca740298g7b2cg4197g988egbf632ea67df6": ["Like hell I won't.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "b8aadc22-f3ef-8a5b-ef92-e1a6877b1285"], "h745bba11gd019g4ec1g91b9g3989b6e4dfee": ["Get out of my way. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsAvenge.html", "bffbb908-897a-b787-f57f-e7df3211797f"]}